OL,3,CMother-of-two honoured in book of
OL,4,Ccondolences after Derry murder
OL,6,FAmy Doherty's murder has led to an
OL,7,Foutpouring of grief.
OL,9,FA book of condolence has been opened
OL,10,Fin memory of the 28-year-old, where
OL,11,Fpeople shared messages of sympathy and
OL,12,Fhope that attacks against women will
OL,13,Fstop.
OL,15,FThe mum-of-two young children was
OL,16,Ffatally injured in her own home on
OL,17,FSaturday.
OL,19,FAmy is the 30th woman murdered in
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland since 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
