OL,3,CMother-of-two honoured in book of
OL,4,Ccondolences after Derry murder
OL,6,FCllr Ruairi McHugh, Mayor of Derry
OL,7,FCity and Strabane said: "We decided,
OL,8,Fas a council and as the Mayor of the
OL,9,Fcity and district, to open this book
OL,10,Fof condolence to allow the community
OL,11,Fto register their sympathy for Amy,
OL,12,Fbut also to show their shock and the
OL,13,Fhorror at what transpired on Saturday."
OL,15,FFor three days, the scene at Summer
OL,16,FMeadows Mews has remained sealed off.
