OL,3,CMother-of-two honoured in book of
OL,4,Ccondolences after Derry murder
OL,6,FIt's understood a 30-year-old man
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of Amy's murder,
OL,8,Fis receiving medical treatment after
OL,9,Freportedly surviving a fall from the
OL,10,FFoyle Bridge.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, it's been announced that
OL,13,FAmy's funeral will take place on
OL,14,FThursday morning.
OL,16,FPlans are also being put in place for
OL,17,Fa candlelight vigil which will be held
OL,18,Fin Guildhall Square on Friday evening.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
